399
00:23:47,780 --> 00:23:49,880
What are you trying to say?

400
00:23:57,350 --> 00:23:58,480
I need a babysitter.

401
00:24:01,360 --> 00:24:02,480
Baby...

402
00:24:03,940 --> 00:24:05,200
Babysitter?

403
