and ragged clothes.

530
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:06,600
Just like I am now.

531
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:07,600
Wei Lin.

532
00:29:07,950 --> 00:29:09,600
I think...

533
00:29:10,180 --> 00:29:12,360
